只是俄罗斯手中剩余的10万多平方公里土地中的一小部分。但加速带来了希望。</p><figure> <span itemscope="" itemprop="image" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" data-slim="0"><meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.economist.com/img/b/1280/2294/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.economist.com/img/b/1280/2294/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png" srcset="https://www.economist.com/img/b/200/358/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 200w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/300/538/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 300w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/400/717/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 400w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/600/1075/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 600w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/640/1147/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 640w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/800/1434/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 800w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/1000/1792/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 1000w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/1280/2294/90/sites/default/files/images/2021/12/articles/body/20230902_wof911.png 1280w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 640px, 95vw" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></figure><p class="article__body-text"><span>最近来自南部前线的消息也是如此。乌克兰攻击的重点现在似乎集中在扎波罗热市以南。 8 月 28 日，在多条战线经过三个月的艰苦奋战后，乌克兰军队解放了主攻轴线沿线的一个约有 500 人的罗布坦村庄。它的占领意味着乌克兰军队终于到达了所谓的苏罗维金线，即俄罗斯在该地区的主要防御工事线。俄罗斯将其资源集中在第一道防线上（见地图）。这可能会让乌克兰人处于突破的边缘：超过这一点，俄罗斯的防御就会更薄弱，而他们希望的储备也会更薄弱。</span></p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Mon, 04 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> /内容/phkkqjq2j455o4qf1e279gv5v2r91fj5</guid><link/> https://www.economist.com/espressochart/2023<category>不确定</category><category>联合国</category><category>刚果民主共和国</category><cat